. Dolphins-at-sunrise boat trips (decreasingly ethical with too many boats; consider whether to participate). The reef snorkeling here is genuinely good.]]></description><Point><coordinates>115.025000,-8.158300,0</coordinates></Point></Placemark></Folder>
